name: cult7.wad
description: This is Map 07 of a Megawad I'm building. After finishing Maps 01-06 I put them into a forum for play-testing. I recieved some comments and tips and tried to follow them with this sequel. So, don't hesitate to tell me your opinion about this map! The story will go on. Maps 01 to 06 contain your trip, starting in a convent, through a church, a big valley, where you find a ship. With the ship you make your way over the ocean to an unknown island. On this island you come to a big castle, which is: this Map! (see "The Story")
